## DATABASE MODELS (Create Dart classes with JSON serialization)

### User Model
- id (String, UUID)
- role (String: 'passenger' or 'driver')
- phone (String, unique)
- email (String, optional)
- fullName (String)
- avatarUrl (String, optional)
- rating (double, default 0.0)
- walletBalance (double, default 0.0)
- isVerified (bool, default false)
- createdAt (DateTime)

### Booking Model  
- id (String, UUID)
- passengerId (String)
- driverId (String, optional)
- pickupLocation (LatLng)
- dropoffLocation (LatLng)
- pickupAddress (String)
- dropoffAddress (String)
- status (String: 'pending', 'accepted', 'arrived', 'started', 'completed', 'cancelled')
- fareEstimate (double)
- finalFare (double, optional)
- paymentMethod (String: 'cash', 'card', 'wallet')
- pickupVerificationCode (String, 4-digit)
- createdAt (DateTime)
- startedAt (DateTime, optional)
- completedAt (DateTime, optional)

### Driver Model (extends User)
- licenseNumber (String)
- licensePhotoUrl (String)
- selfiePhotoUrl (String)
- isApproved (bool)
- isOnline (bool)
- currentLocation (LatLng, optional)
- totalEarnings (double)

