## FEATURE IMPLEMENTATION ORDER

### PHASE 1: Core Setup & Authentication
1. **Supabase Configuration**
   - Initialize Supabase in main.dart with your project URL and anon key
   - Set up auth state listener
   - Implement Row Level Security compatible queries

2. **Authentication Flow**
   - Phone number login with OTP (Supabase Auth)
   - Email fallback option
   - Role selection screen after first login (passenger/driver)
   - Profile creation with name and optional photo
   - Persistent login state using Riverpod

3. **Role Detection & Routing**
   - Check user role from Supabase profiles table
   - Redirect to appropriate dashboard (passenger or driver)
   - Prevent role switching without re-authentication

### PHASE 2: Passenger Features
4. **Ride Booking Flow**
   - Google Maps with current location
   - Search pickup location (autocomplete from Google Places API)
   - Search dropoff location
   - Show fare estimate based on distance calculation
   - Vehicle type selection (standard, premium, large)
   - Confirm booking button creates record in Supabase

5. **Real-time Tracking**
   - After booking accepted, show live driver location
   - Subscribe to Supabase Realtime for driver location updates
   - Show ETA using Google Maps Distance Matrix API
   - Display driver info (name, rating, vehicle, plate number)
   - Cancel trip button (within first 2 minutes only)

6. **Payment & Wallet**
   - Display wallet balance from Supabase
   - Add money to wallet (simulate or integrate Stripe)
   - Select payment method (cash/card/wallet)
   - Show payment confirmation screen after trip
   - Transaction history

7. **Ride History & Ratings**
   - List past trips with details
   - Rate driver (1-5 stars with optional comment)
   - View past receipts
   - Re-book option for frequent routes

8. **Additional Passenger Features**
   - Saved locations (home, work, favorites)
   - Promo code input & validation
   - SOS button (sends alert to emergency contacts + driver)
   - Trip sharing via WhatsApp (deep link with real-time location)
   - Pickup verification code (4-digit PIN shown to passenger)
   - In-app support chat (using Supabase Realtime)
   - Lost & found report form

### PHASE 3: Driver Features
9. **Driver Registration & Verification**
   - Multi-step form (license, vehicle registration, selfie)
   - Upload documents to Supabase Storage
   - Verification pending screen
   - Admin approval required before going online

10. **Online/Offline Mode**
    - Toggle switch to appear online
    - When online, send current location to Supabase every 3 seconds
    - When offline, stop location updates
    - Auto-offline after 15 minutes of no ride requests

11. **Ride Request Handling**
    - Real-time ride request listener (Supabase Realtime)
    - Card pops up with passenger info, pickup/dropoff, fare estimate
    - Accept/Reject buttons
    - 30-second timeout auto-reject
    - Prevent multiple active rides

12. **Active Trip Management**
    - Navigation to pickup location (open Google Maps or use built-in)
    - "Arrived at Pickup" button
    - Enter passenger verification code (matches passenger's PIN)
    - "Start Trip" button after code verified
    - Navigation to dropoff
    - "Complete Trip" button at destination
    - Show final fare (with optional adjustments for waiting time)

13. **Earnings Dashboard**
    - Today's earnings
    - Weekly total
    - Trip history with breakdown
    - Withdrawal button (to Stripe Connect)
    - Earnings chart (last 7 days)

### PHASE 4: Cross-Cutting Features
14. **Real-time Chat**
    - In-app messaging between passenger and driver during active trip
    - Supabase Realtime for instant messages
    - Read receipts
    - Typing indicator

15. **Notifications**
    - OneSignal setup with FCM fallback
    - Push notifications for:
      - Ride accepted/rejected
      - Driver arrived
      - Trip started/completed
      - Payment receipt
      - Promo code offers

16. **Background Location (Driver Only)**
    - Use background_locator package
    - Continue sending location when app is in background
    - Battery optimization handling
    - Permission management

